Description: Halfeti draws inspiration from the lavish goods traded with Turkey: exotic florals, spices, soft leathers and precious fabrics. The fragrance is named for the small Turkish village of Halfeti, where enchanting 'black' roses grow on the banks of the Euphrates river. Dark and mysterious, the roses are an intense shade of crimson, so dusky they appear to be black. Halfeti is an exquisitely opulent woody floral, dazzling in the glow of luxurious golden saffron, decorated with bright citrus, green armoise and woody cypress. An exquisitely multifaceted rose is set like a precious jewel amongst a silken bouquet of sweet florals. The women that wear Balenciaga Paris L'essence are the type of people you want to know. You highly respect them and would also love to be seen with them. Oliver Polge created this scent with that concept in mind. There are scent notes of patchouli, violet, green notes, sandalwood, cedar, and vetiver.The scent represents the woman that it is meant for--passionate, beautiful, and magnetic in nature. If this is the kind of woman you are, then you simply must try this fragrance! If you have a special woman like this in your life you need to let her know that you are very aware of her amazing nature by presenting her with Balenciaga Paris L'essence Eau de Parfume as a gift.
